&lt;div class="alert alert-secondary d-flex align-items-center" role="alert"&gt;
 &lt;div&gt;
 &lt;img width="100px" src="https://mevislab.github.io/examples/pull/123/images/youtube.svg" /&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://youtube.com/shorts/U23QH2Pvwew" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;img width="100px" src="https://img.youtube.com/vi/U23QH2Pvwew/0.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;We have a Short video showing the possibilities of the &lt;b&gt;MeVis Path Tracer&lt;/b&gt; on &lt;a href="https://youtube.com/shorts/U23QH2Pvwew" target="_blank"&gt;YouTube&lt;/a&gt;.
